g.text: ##### condition is the symptom to evaluate
# volume usage should be less than 80%
##### action is the action to perform when condition is true
root@kubemaster# watch kubectl describe storagepolicy volume-resize | grep alerts
Watching Deployment Postgres. Alerts: Warning space usage at 70%
Watching Deployment Postgres. Alerts: Warning space usage at 80%
Watching Deployment Postgres. Alerts: Warning space usage at 90, will resize volume now.
Watching Deployment Postgres. Alerts: Auto resizing volume by 10GB
